import React from "react";
import {Grid, Image, Divider} from 'semantic-ui-react'

const ResumeComponent = () => (
	<Grid textAlign="center" columns={2}>
		<Grid.Row>
			<Grid.Row>
				Marvin Moise Title
				<Grid.Row>Linkedin</Grid.Row>
				<Grid.Row>
					<Grid.Column>Email</Grid.Column>
					<Grid.Column>cell</Grid.Column>
				</Grid.Row>
			</Grid.Row>
			<Grid.Row>
				<Divider />
			</Grid.Row>
			<Grid.Row>
				<Grid.Column>df</Grid.Column>
			</Grid.Row>
		</Grid.Row>
	</Grid>
);

export default ResumeComponent;
